---
// Slide19
---
<section class="slide-container wheel-slide">
      <span class="slide-number"></span>
      <h2 style="justify-content: center;"><i class="fa-solid fa-dharmachakra"></i> Колесо идей</h2>
      <p style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 16px; color: #475569;">Давайте выберем, какой сайт мы создадим сегодня!</p>

      <div style="display: flex; gap: 48px; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin-top: 32px; width: 100%; height: 100%;">
        <div class="wheel-wrapper" style="position: relative; width: 400px; height: 400px; filter: drop-shadow(0 15px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1));">
          <canvas id="wheelCanvas" width="400" height="400"></canvas>
          <div class="wheel-pointer" style="position: absolute; top: -25px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); font-size: 64px; color: #4f46e5; z-index: 10; filter: drop-shadow(0 10px 15px rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.3));"><i class="fa-solid fa-caret-down"></i></div>
        </div>

        <div class="wheel-controls" style="background: #ffffff; padding: 40px; border-radius: 24px; box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.08); width: 380px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 20px;">
          <h3 style="margin: 0; color: #1e293b; font-size: 1.4rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-list-ol" style="color: #4f46e5;"></i> Список идей</h3>
          <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 0.9rem; color: #64748b;">Впишите варианты сайтов (каждый с новой строки):</p>
          <textarea id="wheelIdeas" rows="5" placeholder="Салон красоты&#10;Фотограф&#10;Кофейня" style="width: 100%; padding: 16px; border-radius: 12px; border: 2px solid #e2e8f0; resize: vertical; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1rem; color: #334155; background: #f8fafc; transition: all 0.2s; outline: none;"></textarea>
          <button id="spinBtn" class="nav-btn" style="justify-content: center; padding: 18px; font-size: 1.2rem; width: 100%; box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.3);">Крутить колесо! <i class="fa-solid fa-rotate"></i></button>
          
          <div id="wheelResult" style="margin-top: 8px; font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.3rem; color: #4f46e5; text-align: center; min-height: 2.6rem; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; border-radius: 12px; padding: 8px; opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.3s ease; background: rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.1);"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
